Dear Raffaella,

We have now uploaded all the documentation and correspondence we have on re=
cord. Please take note that there might be a lot of duplicates because of s=
taff being CC'd into emails.

Please make use of this link below to gain access:
https://towernz.sharefile.com/d-s5e9753b3b30d40a9a6c1b57e9a5b6630

If you have any questions or need assistance, please do not hesitate to con=
tact us.

Warm regards
[cid:image001.png@01DC524F.43E83E20]
Privacy Team
Level 5, 136 Fanshawe Street,
PO Box 90347, Auckland 1142
[Text  Description automatically generated with low confidence]
Fair Insurance Code
Tower is a member of the Insurance Council of New Zealand (ICNZ).
We abide by the ICNZ Fair Insurance Code<https://www.icnz.org.nz/fair-insur=
ance-code/>.

Tower holds a Financial Advice Provider licence, issued by the Financial Ma=
rkets Authority.
Our Nominated Representatives may provide financial advice on insurance pro=
ducts provided by Tower.
Tower Insurance is a member of the Insurance and Financial Services Ombudsm=
an Scheme.
Please click here<https://www.tower.co.nz/about-us/publicly-available-discl=
osure/> for our publicly available disclosure document.
Privacy Disclaimer: This email and its attachments are confidential. If you=
 are not the intended recipient,
please notify the sender and delete this email. Unauthorised use or disclos=
ure is prohibited.
Tower Insurance takes your privacy seriously. For more information, please =
refer to our Privacy Statement.<https://www.tower.co.nz/terms-and-condition=
s/>



Classification: Sensitive
From: Privacy
Sent: Friday, 7 November 2025 12:39 pm
To: raffaellanz@icloud.com
Subject: Privacy Request 3

Dear Raffaella,

Thank you so much for your continued patience and understanding while we wo=
rk through your request.

We truly appreciate the opportunity to gather all the necessary information=
 for you. Unfortunately, due to limited resourcing, we're still working thr=
ough the correspondence and aren't quite finished yet. We're really sorry f=
or the delay and kindly ask for one more week to complete the request.

In the meantime, we've uploaded everything we've been able to obtain so far=
. You can access the documents via the link provided. The newly gathered in=
formation is stored in a folder titled "Request 3."
https://towernz.sharefile.com/d-s5e9753b3b30d40a9a6c1b57e9a5b6630

We look forward to your response and apologise for the inconvenience.

Warm regards
[cid:image001.png@01DC524F.43E83E20]
Privacy Team
Level 5, 136 Fanshawe Street,
PO Box 90347, Auckland 1142
[Text    Description automatically generated with low confidence]
