________________________________

The information contained in this email message is confidential and may be =
legally privileged. If you are not the intended recipient, please note that=
 any use, dissemination, distribution, or reproduction of this message in a=
ny form whatsoever, is strictly prohibited. If you received this email in e=
rror, please notify me by return email, delete your copy, and accept my apo=
logies for any inconvenience caused. Please note that your receipt of this =
email from a Tower email address does not constitute our consent for you to=
 send any other electronic information to Tower by return, unless specifica=
lly stated otherwise.

